data.description: Unbeatable location! Centrally located in West Palm Beach's ''The Square,'' this gorgeous CBS townhome offers an upscale, desirable lifestyle. Walk to the finest shops, restaurants and attractions. Enjoy active, coastal living with close proximity to beautiful beaches and the intracoastal. Roof was recently replaced in 2022 and windows are hurricane impact glass. The kitchen features desirable white cabinets, durable granite along with newer stainless steel appliances. Three bedrooms and three full bathrooms boast plenty of space. Oversized living room is perfect for entertaining. Step outside your front door and take a dip in the luxurious, heated pool or relax in the serene courtyard. Make parking in the city easy with your two car garage located behind the security gate. Easily accessible to the surrounding cities, walk to the Brightline train for work or exploration. This is your opportunity to own a rarely available townhome in paradise!
